{"tid":430488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赴韓整容後臉部腫脹　中國女子無法出境","createTime":"2017-10-09T23:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T23:46:18.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42adfaf1b3d26cee2f597d0c27a325f58d148381","tid":430488,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T23:46:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">赴韓整容後臉部腫脹　中國女子無法出境</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171009/s00004/03b2fca9a04afe6430bbce18d77ec4e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171009%2Fs00004%2F03b2fca9a04afe6430bbce18d77ec4e0.jpg&h=e1486fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國為期八天的十一黃金周長假剛結束，有內地人過去幾日把握時間到韓國整容，不過有人整容後因臉部腫脹未及復原，樣子跟證件照片相差太遠，以致在當地機場無法能出境，需要等待確認身分。<br />\n<br />\n中國天氣女主播建華華在微博上發文及張貼照片，指有民航人士傳相給她。相片顯示3名女子頭上綁有紗布，臉部腫脹，容貌怪異。<br />\n<br />\n建華華微博稱，有3名中國女子利用長假期到韓國整容，因為整容手術結束不久，沒有足夠時間復原，回程時在韓國機場無法出境，需要花時間確認身分。<br />\n<br />\n有網友形容自己「笑到快哭」，更稱「對不起我笑到要下獄」。不過也有網友覺得3名女子很可憐，又指「人家不過是整了容，沒必要發照片接受大家的嘲笑吧」。<br />\n<br />\n（東森新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171009/s00004/1507540031626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171009%2Fs00004%2F1507540031626&d=4LEb4YyAUYZV8NcSq2UbhmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=b0335295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171009%2Fs00004%2F1507540031626&h=29ad63b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171009/s00004/1507540031626</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}